graph TD
    A[Incoming Alert] --> B{severity?}

    B -->|critical| C[Critical Route<br/>group_wait: 10s<br/>repeat_interval: 1h]
    B -->|warning| D[Warning Route<br/>group_wait: 30s<br/>repeat_interval: 4h]
    B -->|info| E[Info Route<br/>group_wait: 1m<br/>repeat_interval: 12h]

    C --> F{alert type?}
    F -->|SLO burn rate| G[PagerDuty<br/>Immediate page]
    F -->|pod crash loop| G
    F -->|error rate > 10%| G
    F -->|node down| G

    D --> H{alert type?}
    H -->|high latency| I[Slack #alerts-warning]
    H -->|disk > 80%| I
    H -->|memory > 85%| I
    H -->|pod restarts| I

    E --> J[Email<br/>Platform team DL]

    subgraph "Inhibition Rules"
        K[Critical active?] -->|yes| L[Suppress matching warnings]
        M[Node down?] -->|yes| N[Suppress pod alerts on that node]
    end

    style G fill:#e74c3c,color:#fff
    style I fill:#f39c12,color:#fff
    style J fill:#3498db,color:#fff
